quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  43,11,"Wallathee nazzala mina assama-imaan biqadarin faansharna bihi baldatan maytan kathalikatukhrajoon"
  43,12,"Wallathee khalaqa al-azwajakullaha wajaAAala lakum mina alfulki wal-anAAamima tarkaboon"
  43,13,"Litastawoo AAala thuhoorihithumma tathkuroo niAAmata rabbikum itha istawaytumAAalayhi wataqooloo subhana allathee sakhkhara lanahatha wama kunna lahu muqrineen"
  43,14,"Wa-inna ila rabbinalamunqaliboon"
  43,15,"WajaAAaloo lahu min AAibadihi juz-aninna al-insana lakafoorun mubeen"
  43,16,"Ami ittakhatha mimma yakhluqubanatin waasfakum bilbaneen"
  43,17,"Wa-itha bushshira ahaduhum bimadaraba lirrahmani mathalan thallawajhuhu muswaddan wahuwa katheem"
  43,18,"Awaman yunashshao fee alhilyatiwahuwa fee alkhisami ghayru mubeen"
  43,19,"WajaAAaloo almala-ikata allatheenahum AAibadu arrahmani inathanashahidoo khalqahum satuktabu shahadatuhum wayus-aloon"
  43,20,"Waqaloo law shaa arrahmanuma AAabadnahum ma lahum bithalika minAAilmin in hum illa yakhrusoon"
  43,21,"Am ataynahum kitabanmin qablihi fahum bihi mustamsikoon"
  43,22,"Bal qaloo inna wajadna abaanaAAala ommatin wa-inna AAala atharihimmuhtadoon"
